satellite.heading: Satelles
satellite.specs:
Dimensiones: 50x58x64 mm
1P PocketQube
Pondus: 245 grammata
Materiae: aluminium, aurum, fibra vitrea, et partes electronicae.
Orbita: Altitudo 525 ± 25 km; inclinatio: SSO 97.6 ± 0.1°
Immissio: PSLV (Vehiculum Immissionis Satellitum Polaris) ab ISRO operatum

antenna.heading: Antenna/Sculptura
antenna.specs:
Dimensiones: 6 m (diametro) et 1.2 m (altitudo)
Pondus: 46 kg
Materiae: aluminium, tabula epoxy speculata, tholus aluminii aurei per structuram machinae ligneae suspensus.
